+    // note: for server clock manager autosave
+    /*
+        we call "packState" in "ServerClockManager" in the codec, which
+        is a mapped version of all the clocks into their packed form
+        which the packed form takes the values from the unpacked form,
+        which is only mutated on the global tick and on load of the clock
+        which is at startup. the actual registered clocks are also
+        immutable after init of the clock manager instance, so we can be
